        <titleType>Official Title as Introduced</titleType>
        <title>To amend title XI of the Social Security Act to prohibit any conditions of participation under the Medicare or Medicaid programs that include a vaccine or drug mandate.</title>
        <billTextVersionName>Introduced in House</billTextVersionName>
